# Quick changelog.
- If using Visual Studio Code, install the "Live Server" extension or it will not properly import modules (word-bank.js)
- Added a setting for a blue underline/color of the current character you are on.

- Made it so the website scales a bit better when shrinking window size.
- Changes how spans and input are read so I can make the visuals more cohesive (scaling the page will work pretty well with odd window sizes)
- Added two working buttons to reset the score and displayed word, and another for opening settings.
    * The settings only has two properly tracked options.
    * Reset score can be configured, meaning you can keep score with a reset button hit (only changes displayed word) and keep the score, or reset the score to zero and change displayed word.

